===Etymology===
The word Wales comes from the [[Saxon]] for "foreigner", and is cognate with [[Wallonia]].

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Welsh'''
#(''in plural'') The people of [[Wales]]
# the Welsh [[language]]

